1:97.description:
Icon with Custom Size - Default 16px
Edit width/height layer to override width/height
It's recommend to use custom size icon in component with multi variants/states and icon size can be customized in the instance. It will keep the icon and icon size consistent when switch between variants.

Size adjuster is used for adjust <-> width / ↕︎ height of elements in some special cases. Eg: To set min-width, min-height for auto layout that hug content.
The width/height of adjuster can be changed in auto layout spacing setting.
